Use the OZOM Skill to help you control your smart devices.

(1). Download the "OZOM 2.0" App from your Appstore;
(2). Create an account in "OZOM 2.0 ";
(3). Add devices to our App "OZOM 2.0" and name your devices as you wish;
(4). Download the Alexa App;
(5). Configure your smartphone with Alexa;
(6). Search the "OZOM" skill in Alexa;
(7). Activate the "OZOM" skill,
(8). Login using you OZOM credentials, and you are ready!.

